The paper deals with the task of image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). However, the paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to combine text and image, which suggests it could also belong to the subfield of NLP (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves learning a similarity metric and embedding function, which are common techniques in information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also evaluates its approach on multiple datasets, which suggests it could belong to the subfield of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques to learn the similarity metric and embedding function, which suggests it could also belong to the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG).
